&lt;h1 id="do-animals-laugh"&gt;Do Animals Laugh?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nov 29 2005&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Almost everything that women like in men seems to have some reproductive fitness signaling value. What about humor? Note that it&amp;rsquo;s not enough to say that &amp;ldquo;humor is a stress reliever.&amp;rdquo; The question is, why would it relieve stress?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Natural Beauty</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/natural-beauty/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Nov 2005 12:50:39 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/natural-beauty/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/natural-beauty.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
